# Desired names stored in variables
name1 <- "foo"
name2 <- "bar"

# Yucky base:
list(1, 2) |>
  setNames(c(name1, name2))
#> $foo
#> [1] 1
#> 
#> $bar
#> [1] 2

# Nice {rlang}:
rlang::list2("{name1}" := 1, "{name2}" := 2)
#> $foo
#> [1] 1
#> 
#> $bar
#> [1] 2
